{"pageProps":{"data":[{"id":1,"index":{"entry_number":1,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"フシギダネ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/1.png","genus":"たねポケモン","flavorText":"生まれたときから　背中に\n不思議な　タネが　植えてあって\n体と　ともに　育つという。"},{"id":2,"index":{"entry_number":2,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"フシギソウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/2.png","genus":"たねポケモン","flavorText":"つぼみが　背中に　ついていて\n養分を　吸収していくと\n大きな　花が　咲くという。"},{"id":3,"index":{"entry_number":3,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"フシギバナ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/3.png","genus":"たねポケモン","flavorText":"大きな　花びらを　広げ\n太陽の　光を　浴びていると\n体に　元気が　みなぎっていく。"},{"id":4,"index":{"entry_number":4,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ヒトカゲ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/4.png","genus":"とかげポケモン","flavorText":"尻尾の　炎は\nヒトカゲの　生命力の　証。\n元気だと　さかんに　燃えさかる。"},{"id":5,"index":{"entry_number":5,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"リザード","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/5.png","genus":"かえんポケモン","flavorText":"尻尾を　振り回して\n相手を　なぎ倒し　鋭い　ツメで\nズタズタに　ひきさいてしまう。"},{"id":6,"index":{"entry_number":6,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"リザードン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/6.png","genus":"かえんポケモン","flavorText":"口から　灼熱の　炎を　吐き出すとき\n尻尾の　先は\nより　赤く　激しく　燃え上がる。"},{"id":7,"index":{"entry_number":7,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゼニガメ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/7.png","genus":"かめのこポケモン","flavorText":"甲羅に　閉じこもり　身を　守る。\n相手の　すきを　見逃さず\n水を　噴き出して　反撃する。"},{"id":8,"index":{"entry_number":8,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カメール","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/8.png","genus":"かめポケモン","flavorText":"ポカンと　頭を　たたかれるとき\n甲羅に　引っこんで　避ける。でも\nちょっとだけ　尻尾が　出ているよ。"},{"id":9,"index":{"entry_number":9,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カメックス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/9.png","genus":"こうらポケモン","flavorText":"体が　重たく　のしかかって\n相手を　気絶させる。\nピンチのときは　殻に　隠れる。"},{"id":10,"index":{"entry_number":10,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"キャタピー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10.png","genus":"いもむしポケモン","flavorText":"頭の　触覚から\n強烈な　においを　出して\n敵を　追い払い　身を守る。"},{"id":11,"index":{"entry_number":11,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"トランセル","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/11.png","genus":"さなぎポケモン","flavorText":"鋼鉄のように　硬い　殻で\nやわらかい　中身を　守っている。\n進化するまで　じっと　耐えている。"},{"id":12,"index":{"entry_number":12,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"バタフリー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/12.png","genus":"ちょうちょポケモン","flavorText":"花の　ミツが　大好物。\nわずかな　花粉で　花畑の\n場所を　探し出すことが　できる。"},{"id":13,"index":{"entry_number":13,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ビードル","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/13.png","genus":"けむしポケモン","flavorText":"森や　草地に　多く　生息。\n頭の　先に　５センチぐらいの\n小さく　鋭い　毒針を持つ。"},{"id":14,"index":{"entry_number":14,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"コクーン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/14.png","genus":"さなぎポケモン","flavorText":"自分では　ほとんど　動けないが\n危ないときは　硬くなって\n身を守っているようだ。"},{"id":15,"index":{"entry_number":15,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"スピアー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/15.png","genus":"どくばちポケモン","flavorText":"両手と　お尻にある　３本の　毒針で\n相手を　刺して　刺して\n刺しまくって　攻撃する。"},{"id":16,"index":{"entry_number":16,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ポッポ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/16.png","genus":"ことりポケモン","flavorText":"森や　林に　多く　分布。\n地上でも　激しく　はばたいて\n砂を　かけたりする。"},{"id":17,"index":{"entry_number":17,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ピジョン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/17.png","genus":"とりポケモン","flavorText":"足の　ツメが　発達している。\nエサの　タマタマを　つかんで\n１００キロ先の　巣まで　運ぶ。"},{"id":18,"index":{"entry_number":18,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ピジョット","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/18.png","genus":"とりポケモン","flavorText":"エサを　探すとき　水面　すれすれを\n滑るように　飛んで\nコイキングなどを　わしづかみにする。"},{"id":19,"index":{"entry_number":19,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"コラッタ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/19.png","genus":"ねずみポケモン","flavorText":"食べるものが　あるところなら\nどこにだって　生息する。\n１日中　エサを　探している。"},{"id":20,"index":{"entry_number":20,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ラッタ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/20.png","genus":"ねずみポケモン","flavorText":"伸び続ける　前歯を　削るため\n硬い　ものを　かじる　習性。\nブロック塀も　かじって　壊す。"},{"id":21,"index":{"entry_number":21,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"オニスズメ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/21.png","genus":"ことりポケモン","flavorText":"自分の　テリトリーを　守るため\n短い　羽を　はばたかせて\n忙しく　飛び回っている。"},{"id":22,"index":{"entry_number":22,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"オニドリル","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/22.png","genus":"くちばしポケモン","flavorText":"大きな　翼で　大空を\n飛び続けることが　できる。\n１回も　降りなくても　平気だ。"},{"id":23,"index":{"entry_number":23,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"アーボ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/23.png","genus":"へびポケモン","flavorText":"育つほどに　どんどん　長くなる。\nそして　夜中は　木の枝に\nグルグルと　絡まって　休む。"},{"id":24,"index":{"entry_number":24,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"アーボック","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/24.png","genus":"コブラポケモン","flavorText":"お腹の　模様が　怖い　顔に　見える。\n弱い　敵は　その模様を\n見ただけで　逃げ出してしまう。"},{"id":25,"index":{"entry_number":25,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ピカチュウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/25.png","genus":"ねずみポケモン","flavorText":"尻尾を　立てて　まわりの　様子を\n探っていると　ときどき\n雷が　尻尾に　落ちてくる。"},{"id":26,"index":{"entry_number":26,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ライチュウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/26.png","genus":"ねずみポケモン","flavorText":"電気が　たまってくると\n筋肉が　刺激され\nいつもより　攻撃的に　なってしまう。"},{"id":27,"index":{"entry_number":27,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サンド","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/27.png","genus":"ねずみポケモン","flavorText":"地面に　穴を　掘って　住む。\n自分に　危険が　迫ると\nまるくなって　身を　守る。"},{"id":28,"index":{"entry_number":28,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サンドパン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/28.png","genus":"ねずみポケモン","flavorText":"すごい　勢いで　地面を掘ると\nトゲや　ツメが　折れてしまうが\n次の日には　生えそろっている。"},{"id":29,"index":{"entry_number":29,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニドラン♀","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/29.png","genus":"どくばりポケモン","flavorText":"体は　小さくても　毒針を\n持つため　注意が　必要だ。\nメスのほうが　ツノが　小さい。"},{"id":30,"index":{"entry_number":30,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニドリーナ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/30.png","genus":"どくばりポケモン","flavorText":"メスなので　性格は　温厚。\n口から　出す　超音波は\n相手を　まどわす　力がある。"},{"id":31,"index":{"entry_number":31,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニドクイン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/31.png","genus":"ドリルポケモン","flavorText":"ウロコで　覆われた　頑丈な　体で\n巣穴の　入り口を　ふさぎ\n敵から　子供たちを　守る。"},{"id":32,"index":{"entry_number":32,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニドラン♂","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/32.png","genus":"どくばりポケモン","flavorText":"草むらの　上に　耳だけ　出して\nまわりの　気配を　探る。\n猛毒の　ツノで　身を　守る。"},{"id":33,"index":{"entry_number":33,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニドリーノ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/33.png","genus":"どくばりポケモン","flavorText":"発達した　耳を　立てて\nまわりの　気配を　探る。\nなにかあると　すぐに　飛びかかる。"},{"id":34,"index":{"entry_number":34,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニドキング","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/34.png","genus":"ドリルポケモン","flavorText":"石のように　硬い　皮膚と\n長く　伸びた　ツノが　特徴。\nツノには　毒も　あるので　注意。"},{"id":35,"index":{"entry_number":35,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ピッピ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/35.png","genus":"ようせいポケモン","flavorText":"満月の夜　ピッピが　集まって\nダンスを　踊る様子を　見ると\n幸せに　なれると　言われている。"},{"id":36,"index":{"entry_number":36,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ピクシー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/36.png","genus":"ようせいポケモン","flavorText":"１キロ先で　落ちた　針の　音も\n聞き分ける　優れた　耳を　持つ。\n静かな　山奥に　住んでいる。"},{"id":37,"index":{"entry_number":37,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ロコン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/37.png","genus":"きつねポケモン","flavorText":"生まれたとき　尻尾は　真っ白で\n１本しかない。育つと　やがて\n先が　分かれて　尻尾が　増える。"},{"id":38,"index":{"entry_number":38,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"キュウコン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/38.png","genus":"きつねポケモン","flavorText":"黄金に　輝く　体毛と\n９本の　長い　尻尾を　持つ。\n１０００年は　生きると　言われる。"},{"id":39,"index":{"entry_number":39,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"プリン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/39.png","genus":"ふうせんポケモン","flavorText":"まるくて　大きい　瞳で　誘いこみ\n心地よい　歌を　歌い\n相手を　眠らせる。"},{"id":40,"index":{"entry_number":40,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"プクリン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/40.png","genus":"ふうせんポケモン","flavorText":"２匹　寄り添いあうと　お互いの\n毛皮が　気持ち良すぎて\n離れられなく　なってしまう。"},{"id":41,"index":{"entry_number":41,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ズバット","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/41.png","genus":"こうもりポケモン","flavorText":"口から　出す　超音波で\n両目が　なくても\nまわりの　障害物を　察知できる。"},{"id":42,"index":{"entry_number":42,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴルバット","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/42.png","genus":"こうもりポケモン","flavorText":"かみついたら　最後。死ぬほど\n血を　吸いまくるので　重たくなって\n自分で　飛べなくなることもある。"},{"id":43,"index":{"entry_number":43,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ナゾノクサ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/43.png","genus":"ざっそうポケモン","flavorText":"昼間は　太陽を　避けるため\n冷たい　地面に　潜っている。\n月の　光を　浴びて　育つ。"},{"id":44,"index":{"entry_number":44,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"クサイハナ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/44.png","genus":"ざっそうポケモン","flavorText":"猛烈な　クサさ！　それなのに\n１０００人に　１人ぐらい\nこれを　好んで　かぐ　人がいる。"},{"id":45,"index":{"entry_number":45,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ラフレシア","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/45.png","genus":"フラワーポケモン","flavorText":"花びらが　大きいほど\nたくさん　花粉を　出すが\n頭が　重たくて　疲れてしまうという。"},{"id":46,"index":{"entry_number":46,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"パラス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/46.png","genus":"きのこポケモン","flavorText":"虫の　背中に　生えているのは\n冬虫夏草　という　キノコ。\n育つと　キノコも　大きくなる。"},{"id":47,"index":{"entry_number":47,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"パラセクト","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/47.png","genus":"きのこポケモン","flavorText":"体よりも　大きな　キノコが\nパラセクトを　操っている。\n毒の　胞子を　ばらまく。"},{"id":48,"index":{"entry_number":48,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"コンパン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/48.png","genus":"こんちゅうポケモン","flavorText":"小さな　目が　たくさん　集まって\n大きな　目に　なっている。\n夜になると　明かりに　集まる。"},{"id":49,"index":{"entry_number":49,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"モルフォン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/49.png","genus":"どくがポケモン","flavorText":"ばらまかれた　りんぷんに　触れると\n体の　感覚が　おかしくなって\nまっすぐ　立っていられなくなる。"},{"id":50,"index":{"entry_number":50,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ディグダ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/50.png","genus":"もぐらポケモン","flavorText":"地下１メートルくらいを　掘りすすみ\n木の根っこなどを　かじって　生きる。\nたまに　地上に　顔を出す。"},{"id":51,"index":{"entry_number":51,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ダグトリオ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/51.png","genus":"もぐらポケモン","flavorText":"地中を　掘りすすんで\n相手が　油断しているところを\n別の　場所から　攻撃する。"},{"id":52,"index":{"entry_number":52,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニャース","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/52.png","genus":"ばけねこポケモン","flavorText":"夜中に　行動する　習性。\nキラキラ　光るものを　見つけると\n負けないくらい　瞳が　輝く。"},{"id":53,"index":{"entry_number":53,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ペルシアン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/53.png","genus":"シャムネコポケモン","flavorText":"毛並みが　美しく\nペットにしたがる　人も　多いが　すぐ\nひっかいたり　するので　手強いぞ。"},{"id":54,"index":{"entry_number":54,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"コダック","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/54.png","genus":"あひるポケモン","flavorText":"いつも　頭痛に　悩まされている。\nこの　頭痛が　激しくなると\n不思議な　力を　使いはじめる。"},{"id":55,"index":{"entry_number":55,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴルダック","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/55.png","genus":"あひるポケモン","flavorText":"夕暮れ　水辺に　姿をみせる。\n額が　あやしく　光るとき\n神通力を　使いこなすという。"},{"id":56,"index":{"entry_number":56,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"マンキー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/56.png","genus":"ぶたざるポケモン","flavorText":"意味もなく　怒って　暴れ出すと\n仲間の　区別も　つかなくなるので\n近寄るのは　非常に　危険だ。"},{"id":57,"index":{"entry_number":57,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"オコリザル","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/57.png","genus":"ぶたざるポケモン","flavorText":"まわりに　だれも　いないときだけは\n怒るのを　やめている。しかし\nそれを　見るのは　難しい。"},{"id":58,"index":{"entry_number":58,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ガーディ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/58.png","genus":"こいぬポケモン","flavorText":"人懐こく　誠実な　性格。\n敵には　ほえて　かみつき\n追い払おうとする。"},{"id":59,"index":{"entry_number":59,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ウインディ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/59.png","genus":"でんせつポケモン","flavorText":"昔から　多くの　人を\n虜にした　美しい　ポケモン。\n飛ぶように　軽やかに　走る。"},{"id":60,"index":{"entry_number":60,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニョロモ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/60.png","genus":"おたまポケモン","flavorText":"スベスベした　黒い皮膚は　薄く\n湿っている。内臓の　一部が\n透けて　渦巻状に　見える。"},{"id":61,"index":{"entry_number":61,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニョロゾ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/61.png","genus":"おたまポケモン","flavorText":"陸でも　水中でも　暮らせる。\n地上では　いつも　汗をかき\n皮膚を　ぬめぬめ　させている。"},{"id":62,"index":{"entry_number":62,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ニョロボン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/62.png","genus":"おたまポケモン","flavorText":"強靭な　筋肉を　持つ。\n太平洋を　休むことなく\n泳ぎ続けることが　できるのだ。"},{"id":63,"index":{"entry_number":63,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ケーシィ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/63.png","genus":"ねんりきポケモン","flavorText":"１日　１８時間は　寝ている。\n眠ってる　あいだでも\nさまざまな　超能力を　使う。"},{"id":64,"index":{"entry_number":64,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ユンゲラー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/64.png","genus":"ねんりきポケモン","flavorText":"超能力を　発揮すると\n強い　アルファ波を　出して\n精密機械を　壊してしまう。"},{"id":65,"index":{"entry_number":65,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"フーディン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/65.png","genus":"ねんりきポケモン","flavorText":"脳細胞は　いつも　分裂して\n死ぬまで　増え続けるので\nあらゆることを　覚えておける。"},{"id":66,"index":{"entry_number":66,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ワンリキー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/66.png","genus":"かいりきポケモン","flavorText":"ゴローンを　何度も　上げ下ろしして\n全身の　筋肉を　鍛える。\nあらゆる　格闘技を　使う。"},{"id":67,"index":{"entry_number":67,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴーリキー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/67.png","genus":"かいりきポケモン","flavorText":"すごく　強靭な　肉体なので\nパワーセーブ　ベルトを　つけて\n強さを　制御している。"},{"id":68,"index":{"entry_number":68,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カイリキー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/68.png","genus":"かいりきポケモン","flavorText":"発達した　４本の　腕は\n２秒間に　１０００発の　パンチを\n繰り出すことができる。"},{"id":69,"index":{"entry_number":69,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"マダツボミ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/69.png","genus":"フラワーポケモン","flavorText":"ひょろっとした　体つきだが\n獲物を　捕らえるときの　動きは\n目にも　とまらないほど　素早い。"},{"id":70,"index":{"entry_number":70,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ウツドン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/70.png","genus":"ハエとりポケモン","flavorText":"葉っぱの　部分は　カッターになって\n相手を　切り裂く。口からは\nなんでも　溶かす　液体を　吐く。"},{"id":71,"index":{"entry_number":71,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ウツボット","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/71.png","genus":"ハエとりポケモン","flavorText":"ジャングルの　奥地に　ウツボット\nばかり　いる　地帯が　あって\n行ったら　２度と　帰ってこれない。"},{"id":72,"index":{"entry_number":72,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"メノクラゲ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/72.png","genus":"くらげポケモン","flavorText":"体の　ほとんどが　水分。\n水晶のような　目玉から\n不思議な　ビームを　発射する。"},{"id":73,"index":{"entry_number":73,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ドククラゲ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/73.png","genus":"くらげポケモン","flavorText":"触手は　普段　短くて\n獲物を　刺すときに\n長く　伸びて　絡みつくのだ。"},{"id":74,"index":{"entry_number":74,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"イシツブテ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/74.png","genus":"がんせきポケモン","flavorText":"草原や　山に　生息する。\n石ころに　似ていて　気がつかず\n踏んだり　つまずいたりしてしまう。"},{"id":75,"index":{"entry_number":75,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴローン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/75.png","genus":"がんせきポケモン","flavorText":"山から　転がり　落ちるとき\n体の　あちこちが　取れても\n気にしない　豪快な　性格。"},{"id":76,"index":{"entry_number":76,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴローニャ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/76.png","genus":"メガトンポケモン","flavorText":"山頂から　ふもとまで　続く　溝は\nゴローニャが　転がり落ちる\n通り道なので　要注意。"},{"id":77,"index":{"entry_number":77,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ポニータ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/77.png","genus":"ひのうまポケモン","flavorText":"生まれたばかりでは　立つのがやっと。\nだが　走るほどに　足腰は\n鍛えられて　速度が　増していく。"},{"id":78,"index":{"entry_number":78,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ギャロップ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/78.png","genus":"ひのうまポケモン","flavorText":"速く　動く　物体を　見ると\n競争したくなり　猛烈な\nスピードで　追いかけはじめる。"},{"id":79,"index":{"entry_number":79,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ヤドン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/79.png","genus":"まぬけポケモン","flavorText":"いつも　ボーッとしていて　なにを\n考えているか　わからない。\n尻尾で　エサを　釣るのが　得意。"},{"id":80,"index":{"entry_number":80,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ヤドラン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/80.png","genus":"やどかりポケモン","flavorText":"くっついている　シェルダーは\n尻尾から　にじみ出る　うま味が\n欲しくて　ずっと　離れない。"},{"id":81,"index":{"entry_number":81,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"コイル","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/81.png","genus":"じしゃくポケモン","flavorText":"左右の　ユニットから\n重力を　さえぎる　力を\n出すので　空中に　浮かべる。"},{"id":82,"index":{"entry_number":82,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"レアコイル","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/82.png","genus":"じしゃくポケモン","flavorText":"複数の　コイルが　連結して\n強力な　磁力線と\n高電圧を　放射する。"},{"id":83,"index":{"entry_number":83,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カモネギ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/83.png","genus":"かるがもポケモン","flavorText":"持っている　茎は　大切な\n武器でもあり　刀を　振るように\nいろんな　ものを　切ることができる。"},{"id":84,"index":{"entry_number":84,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ドードー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/84.png","genus":"ふたごどりポケモン","flavorText":"突然変異で　見つかった\n２つの　頭を　持つ　ポケモン。\n時速１００キロで　走る。"},{"id":85,"index":{"entry_number":85,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ドードリオ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/85.png","genus":"みつごどりポケモン","flavorText":"３つの　頭が　見ている前で\nわずかでも　すきを　見せると\nクチバシで　激しく　つつかれる。"},{"id":86,"index":{"entry_number":86,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"パウワウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/86.png","genus":"あしかポケモン","flavorText":"氷山で　暮らす　ポケモン。\n頭の　とがった　でっぱりで\n氷を　割って　海を　泳ぐ。"},{"id":87,"index":{"entry_number":87,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ジュゴン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/87.png","genus":"あしかポケモン","flavorText":"全身が　真っ白な　毛で\n覆われている。寒さに　強く\nむしろ　寒いほど　元気になる。"},{"id":88,"index":{"entry_number":88,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ベトベター","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/88.png","genus":"ヘドロポケモン","flavorText":"月からの　エックス線を　浴びた\nヘドロが　ベトベターに　変化した。\n汚いものが　大好物。"},{"id":89,"index":{"entry_number":89,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ベトベトン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/89.png","genus":"ヘドロポケモン","flavorText":"ヘドロが　たまる　くさい　場所を\n好んで　集まってくるので\nあたりは　いっそう　くさくなる。"},{"id":90,"index":{"entry_number":90,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"シェルダー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/90.png","genus":"２まいがいポケモン","flavorText":"硬い　殻は　どんな　攻撃も\n跳ね返す。開いたときに\n中を　攻撃されると　弱い。"},{"id":91,"index":{"entry_number":91,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"パルシェン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/91.png","genus":"２まいがいポケモン","flavorText":"潮の　流れが　激しい　海に\n生息している　パルシェンの\n殻の　トゲは　大きく　鋭い。"},{"id":92,"index":{"entry_number":92,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴース","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/92.png","genus":"ガスじょうポケモン","flavorText":"ガスでできた　薄い　体は\nどんな　大きさの　相手も\n包みこみ　息の根を　止める。"},{"id":93,"index":{"entry_number":93,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゴースト","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/93.png","genus":"ガスじょうポケモン","flavorText":"暗闇で　だれもいないのに\n見られているような　気がしたら\nそこに　ゴーストが　いるのだ。"},{"id":94,"index":{"entry_number":94,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ゲンガー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/94.png","genus":"シャドーポケモン","flavorText":"物陰に　姿を　隠す。\nゲンガーの　潜んでいる　部屋は\n温度が　５度　下がるといわれる。"},{"id":95,"index":{"entry_number":95,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"イワーク","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/95.png","genus":"いわへびポケモン","flavorText":"地中を　ものすごい　勢いで\n掘りすすみ　エサを　探す。通った\n跡は　ディグダの　住処になる。"},{"id":96,"index":{"entry_number":96,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"スリープ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/96.png","genus":"さいみんポケモン","flavorText":"眠らせては　夢を　食べるが\n悪い　夢ばかり　食べてると\nお腹を　壊すことが　あるらしい。"},{"id":97,"index":{"entry_number":97,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"スリーパー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/97.png","genus":"さいみんポケモン","flavorText":"振り子のようなものを　持ち歩く。\n子供に　催眠術を　かけて\nどこかへ　連れ去る　事件があった。"},{"id":98,"index":{"entry_number":98,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"クラブ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/98.png","genus":"さわがにポケモン","flavorText":"危険が　迫ると　口から　吐き出す\n泡で　全身を　包んで\n体を　大きく　みせようとする。"},{"id":99,"index":{"entry_number":99,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"キングラー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/99.png","genus":"はさみポケモン","flavorText":"硬い　ハサミは　１万馬力の\nパワーを　持っているが\n大きすぎて　動きが　鈍い。"},{"id":100,"index":{"entry_number":100,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ビリリダマ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/100.png","genus":"ボールポケモン","flavorText":"モンスターボールが　売り出されたのと\n同じ　時期に　発見された。\nなにか　関係があると　いわれる。"},{"id":101,"index":{"entry_number":101,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"マルマイン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/101.png","genus":"ボールポケモン","flavorText":"少しの　刺激に　反応して\n爆発する。バクダンボールという\nあだ名で　怖がられている。"},{"id":102,"index":{"entry_number":102,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"タマタマ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/102.png","genus":"たまごポケモン","flavorText":"テレパシーで　会話をしているため\nタマタマを　引き離そうとしても\nすぐに　集まって　６匹になる。"},{"id":103,"index":{"entry_number":103,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ナッシー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/103.png","genus":"やしのみポケモン","flavorText":"３つの　頭は　考えることは\n別々でも　仲良しなので\nケンカしたり　しないらしい。"},{"id":104,"index":{"entry_number":104,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カラカラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/104.png","genus":"こどくポケモン","flavorText":"死に別れた　母親の　骨を\n頭に　覆っている。寂しいとき\n大声で　泣くという。"},{"id":105,"index":{"entry_number":105,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ガラガラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/105.png","genus":"ほねずきポケモン","flavorText":"骨に　灯った　呪いの　炎は\nいつまでも　治らない　痛みを\n体と　心に　残すという。"},{"id":106,"index":{"entry_number":106,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サワムラー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/106.png","genus":"キックポケモン","flavorText":"脚が　自由に　伸び縮みして\n遠く　離れている　場合でも\n相手を　蹴り上げることができる。"},{"id":107,"index":{"entry_number":107,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"エビワラー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/107.png","genus":"パンチポケモン","flavorText":"腕を　ねじりながら　繰り出す\nパンチは　コンクリートも　粉砕。\n３分　戦うと　ひとやすみする。"},{"id":108,"index":{"entry_number":108,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ベロリンガ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/108.png","genus":"なめまわしポケモン","flavorText":"長い　舌は　ねばねばした\nだえきで　べっとり。どんなものでも\nくっついて　とても　便利。"},{"id":109,"index":{"entry_number":109,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ドガース","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/109.png","genus":"どくガスポケモン","flavorText":"薄い　バルーン状の　体に\n猛毒の　ガスが　つまっている。\n近くに　来ると　くさい。"},{"id":110,"index":{"entry_number":110,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"マタドガス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/110.png","genus":"どくガスポケモン","flavorText":"どちらかが　ふくらむと　片方は\nしぼむ　双子の　ドガース。いつも\n体内の　毒ガスを　混ぜている。"},{"id":111,"index":{"entry_number":111,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サイホーン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/111.png","genus":"とげとげポケモン","flavorText":"頭は　悪いが　力が　強く\n高層ビルも　体当たりで\nコナゴナに　粉砕する。"},{"id":112,"index":{"entry_number":112,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サイドン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/112.png","genus":"ドリルポケモン","flavorText":"全身を　よろいのような　皮膚で\n守っている。２０００度の\nマグマの　中でも　生きられる。"},{"id":113,"index":{"entry_number":113,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ラッキー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/113.png","genus":"たまごポケモン","flavorText":"幸せを　運ぶと　いわれている。\n傷ついた　人に　タマゴを\n分けてあげる　優しい　ポケモン。"},{"id":114,"index":{"entry_number":114,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"モンジャラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/114.png","genus":"ツルじょうポケモン","flavorText":"たくさんの　うごめく　ツルに\n覆われて　正体不明。\n青いツルは　一生　伸びる。"},{"id":115,"index":{"entry_number":115,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ガルーラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/115.png","genus":"おやこポケモン","flavorText":"お腹の　袋で　子育てをする。\n安全な　ときだけ　子供を\n袋から　出して　遊ばせる。"},{"id":116,"index":{"entry_number":116,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"タッツー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/116.png","genus":"ドラゴンポケモン","flavorText":"水面から　勢いよく　墨を　発射して\n飛んでいる　虫を\n撃ち落とすことがあるという。"},{"id":117,"index":{"entry_number":117,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"シードラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/117.png","genus":"ドラゴンポケモン","flavorText":"うかつに　触ろうとすると\n体中に　生える　トゲに　刺されて\n気絶することもある。"},{"id":118,"index":{"entry_number":118,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"トサキント","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/118.png","genus":"きんぎょポケモン","flavorText":"５ノットの　スピードで　泳ぐ。\n身の　危険を　感じると\n鋭い　ツノで　反撃する。"},{"id":119,"index":{"entry_number":119,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"アズマオウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/119.png","genus":"きんぎょポケモン","flavorText":"秋が　くると　産卵のために\n流れに　逆らって　力強く\n川を　泳ぐ　姿が　みられる。"},{"id":120,"index":{"entry_number":120,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ヒトデマン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/120.png","genus":"ほしがたポケモン","flavorText":"体の　中心で　光る\nコアが　ある限り\n体が　ちぎれても　再生できる。"},{"id":121,"index":{"entry_number":121,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"スターミー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/121.png","genus":"なぞのポケモン","flavorText":"真ん中の　コアと呼ばれる　部分は\n七色に　輝く。これを\n宝石にする　人も　いるという。"},{"id":122,"index":{"entry_number":122,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"バリヤード","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/122.png","genus":"バリアーポケモン","flavorText":"指先から　出す　波動が\n空気を　固めて　壁を　作る。\n激しい　攻撃も　跳ね返す。"},{"id":123,"index":{"entry_number":123,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ストライク","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/123.png","genus":"かまきりポケモン","flavorText":"鋭い　カマで　獲物を　切り裂き\n息の根を　止める。ごくまれに\n羽を　使って　飛ぶ。"},{"id":124,"index":{"entry_number":124,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ルージュラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/124.png","genus":"ひとがたポケモン","flavorText":"腰を　振るように　歩いている。\n油断をすると　思わず　釣られて\n踊ってしまうという。"},{"id":125,"index":{"entry_number":125,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"エレブー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/125.png","genus":"でんげきポケモン","flavorText":"体の　表面には　電気が\n流れている。あたりが　暗いと\n全身が　青白く　光るのだ。"},{"id":126,"index":{"entry_number":126,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ブーバー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/126.png","genus":"ひふきポケモン","flavorText":"火山の　火口近くで　見つかった。\n口から　炎を　吐く。\n体温は　１２００度もある。"},{"id":127,"index":{"entry_number":127,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カイロス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/127.png","genus":"くわがたポケモン","flavorText":"２本の　ツノで　獲物を　挟んで\nちぎれるまで　放さない。ちぎれない\nときは　かなたまで　投げ飛ばすのだ。"},{"id":128,"index":{"entry_number":128,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ケンタロス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/128.png","genus":"あばれうしポケモン","flavorText":"３本の　尻尾で　自分を　たたき\n戦う　気持ちを　高めると\n全速力で　突っこんでくる。"},{"id":129,"index":{"entry_number":129,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"コイキング","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/129.png","genus":"さかなポケモン","flavorText":"力も　スピードも　ほとんど　ダメ。\n世界で　一番　弱くて\n情けない　ポケモンだ。"},{"id":130,"index":{"entry_number":130,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ギャラドス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/130.png","genus":"きょうあくポケモン","flavorText":"争いの　起こった　村を\n焼きつくしたという　記録が\n古文書に　残されている。"},{"id":131,"index":{"entry_number":131,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ラプラス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/131.png","genus":"のりものポケモン","flavorText":"優しい　心の　持ち主。\nめったに　争わないため　たくさん\n捕まえられ　数が　減った。"},{"id":132,"index":{"entry_number":132,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"メタモン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/132.png","genus":"へんしんポケモン","flavorText":"体の　細胞の　作りを\n自分で　組み替えて\nほかの　生命体に　変身する。"},{"id":133,"index":{"entry_number":133,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"イーブイ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/133.png","genus":"しんかポケモン","flavorText":"進化のとき　姿と　能力が\n変わることで　きびしい　環境に\n対応する　珍しい　ポケモン。"},{"id":134,"index":{"entry_number":134,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"シャワーズ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/134.png","genus":"あわはきポケモン","flavorText":"きれいな　水辺を　好んでいる。\n細胞が　水の　分子に　似ており\n水に　溶けることもできる。"},{"id":135,"index":{"entry_number":135,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サンダース","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/135.png","genus":"かみなりポケモン","flavorText":"体内に　電気が　たまると\n全身の　体毛が　全部\n鋭く　とがりはじめる。"},{"id":136,"index":{"entry_number":136,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ブースター","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/136.png","genus":"ほのおポケモン","flavorText":"体内に　炎袋を　持つ。\n戦いが　はじまる　直前には\n体温が　９００度まで　上がる。"},{"id":137,"index":{"entry_number":137,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ポリゴン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/137.png","genus":"バーチャルポケモン","flavorText":"研究の末　生み出された\n人工の　ポケモン。基本的な\n動作しか　プログラムされていない。"},{"id":138,"index":{"entry_number":138,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"オムナイト","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/138.png","genus":"うずまきポケモン","flavorText":"大昔　海に　住んでいた\n古代ポケモン。１０本の　脚を\nくねらせて　泳ぐ。"},{"id":139,"index":{"entry_number":139,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"オムスター","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/139.png","genus":"うずまきポケモン","flavorText":"触手が　手足のように\n発達している。しがみつくと\n同時に　かみついてくる。"},{"id":140,"index":{"entry_number":140,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カブト","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/140.png","genus":"こうらポケモン","flavorText":"３億年前の　砂浜で\n暮らしていたと　考えられている。\n硬い　殻が　身を　守る。"},{"id":141,"index":{"entry_number":141,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カブトプス","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/141.png","genus":"こうらポケモン","flavorText":"水中を　移動するとき\n手足を　小さく　折りたたみ\n甲羅を　くねらせ　速く　泳ぐ。"},{"id":142,"index":{"entry_number":142,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"プテラ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/142.png","genus":"かせきポケモン","flavorText":"こはくに　残された　恐竜の\n遺伝子から　復活させた。\n高い　声で　鳴きながら　飛ぶ。"},{"id":143,"index":{"entry_number":143,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カビゴン","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/143.png","genus":"いねむりポケモン","flavorText":"１日に　食べ物を　４００キロ\n食べないと　気がすまない。\n食べ終わると　眠ってしまう。"},{"id":144,"index":{"entry_number":144,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"フリーザー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/144.png","genus":"れいとうポケモン","flavorText":"伝説の　とりポケモン。\n空気中の　水分を　凍らせ\n吹雪を　作り出すことが　できる。"},{"id":145,"index":{"entry_number":145,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"サンダー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/145.png","genus":"でんげきポケモン","flavorText":"雲の　上から　巨大な　稲妻を\n落としながら　現れる\n伝説の　とりポケモンである。"},{"id":146,"index":{"entry_number":146,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ファイヤー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/146.png","genus":"かえんポケモン","flavorText":"昔から　火の鳥伝説として\n知られる。羽ばたくたびに　羽が\n明るく　燃え上がり　美しい。"},{"id":147,"index":{"entry_number":147,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ミニリュウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/147.png","genus":"ドラゴンポケモン","flavorText":"目撃者が　少ないために\n幻のポケモンと　呼ばれていた。\n脱皮した　皮が　見つかっている。"},{"id":148,"index":{"entry_number":148,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ハクリュー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/148.png","genus":"ドラゴンポケモン","flavorText":"水晶のような　玉には\n天候を　自由に　操る\n能力が　秘められているらしい。"},{"id":149,"index":{"entry_number":149,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"カイリュー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/149.png","genus":"ドラゴンポケモン","flavorText":"大きな　体格で　空を　飛ぶ。\n地球を　約１６時間で\n１周してしまう。"},{"id":150,"index":{"entry_number":150,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ミュウツー","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/150.png","genus":"いでんしポケモン","flavorText":"１人の　科学者が　何年も\n恐ろしい　遺伝子　研究を\n続けた　結果　誕生した。"},{"id":151,"index":{"entry_number":151,"pokedex":{"name":"national","url":"https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokedex/1/"}},"name":"ミュウ","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/151.png","genus":"しんしゅポケモン","flavorText":"あらゆる　技を　使うため\nポケモンの　先祖と　考える\n学者が　たくさん　いる。"}],"lang":"ja"},"__N_SSG":true}